#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:3
msgid ""
"From v1.3.0, BPMN processes, form schemas, and document templates are "
"persisted to PostgreSQL via the LDE backend. The frontend uses a **write-"
"through cache with async hydration**: all reads are synchronous from "
"`localStorage` (zero-latency UI), writes update `localStorage` immediately "
"and then POST to the backend in the background, and on editor mount a `GET` "
"hydration call replaces local non-readonly records with the authoritative "
"server state."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:7
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\developer\\asset-storage.md:7"
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:8
msgid ""
"graph TD\n"
"    A[Editor component] -->|mount| B[hydrateFromServer]\n"
"    A -->|save| C[localStorage cache]\n"
"    B -->|background fetch| D[LDE Backend]\n"
"    D --> E[(PostgreSQL — lde_assets)]"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:18
msgid "Write-through cache strategy"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:20
msgid "On **save**, each service:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:22
msgid ""
"Writes the updated record to `localStorage` immediately — the UI reflects "
"the change synchronously with zero latency."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:23
msgid ""
"Fires a background `fetch` to `POST /v1/assets/{type}` — no `await`, no "
"spinner. If the network call fails, a warning is logged to the browser "
"console but the user experience is unaffected."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:25
msgid "On **delete**, each service:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:27
msgid "Removes the record from `localStorage` immediately."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:28
msgid "Fires a background `DELETE /v1/assets/{type}/:id`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:30
msgid ""
"Example assets (`readonly: true`) are never written to the backend. They are "
"seeded on the frontend from static files in `public/examples/` and "
"`defaultTemplates.ts`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:34
msgid "Hydration on mount"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:36
msgid ""
"Each editor component runs a second `useEffect` alongside the example seed "
"effect:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:37
msgid ""
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"  BpmnService.hydrateFromServer().then(setProcesses);\n"
"}, []);"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:43
msgid ""
"`hydrateFromServer()` calls `GET /v1/assets/bpmn`, merges the server "
"response with the local readonly examples, writes the merged list back to "
"`localStorage`, and returns it. If the request fails for any reason the "
"existing `localStorage` contents are returned unchanged and a warning is "
"logged."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:45
msgid ""
"This means the editor always starts from local cache (instant render) and "
"then silently updates with authoritative server data within one network "
"round-trip."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:49
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\developer\\asset-storage.md:49"
msgid "Database schema"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:51
msgid "`process_definitions`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:52
msgid ""
"CREATE TABLE process_definitions (\n"
"  id                     UUID         PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()"
",\n"
"  lde_id                 VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n"
"  bpmn_process_id        VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,\n"
"  name                   VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,\n"
"  description            TEXT,\n"
"  xml                    TEXT         NOT NULL,\n"
"  process_role           VARCHAR(20)  NOT NULL DEFAULT 'standalone'\n"
"                           CHECK (process_role IN ('shell', 'subprocess', "
"'standalone')),\n"
"  called_element         VARCHAR(255),\n"
"  linked_dmn_templates   TEXT[]       NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n"
"  status                 VARCHAR(20)  NOT NULL DEFAULT 'wip'\n"
"                           CHECK (status IN ('example', 'wip')),\n"
"  readonly               BOOLEAN      NOT NULL DEFAULT FALSE,\n"
"  schema_version         INTEGER      NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n"
"  deployed_at            TIMESTAMPTZ,\n"
"  operaton_url           TEXT,\n"
"  operaton_deployment_id TEXT,\n"
"  deployed_forms         TEXT[]       NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n"
"  deployed_documents     TEXT[]       NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',\n"
"  language               VARCHAR(2),                         -- v1.6.0\n"
"  organization           VARCHAR(100),                        -- v1.6.0\n"
"  created_at             TIMESTAMPTZ  NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),\n"
"  updated_at             TIMESTAMPTZ  NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()\n"
");\n"
"\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_pd_bpmn_process_id ON process_definitions (bpmn_process_id)"
";\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_pd_called_element  ON process_definitions (called_element)\n"
"  WHERE called_element IS NOT NULL;\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_pd_process_role    ON process_definitions (process_role);\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_pd_language        ON process_definitions (language)\n"
"  WHERE language IS NOT NULL;\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_pd_organization    ON process_definitions (organization)\n"
"  WHERE organization IS NOT NULL;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:89
msgid ""
"`lde_id` is the internal LDE identifier (e.g. `process_1774384869117`). "
"`bpmn_process_id` is the `<process id=\"...\">` value from the BPMN XML — "
"used for subprocess lookup during bundle assembly."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:91
msgid ""
"`language` (ISO 639-1, nullable) and `organization` (open-ended key, "
"nullable) were added in v1.6.0 to drive list-panel grouping and the deploy-"
"time language consistency check; partial indexes skip the common `NULL` "
"case. See [Multilingualism]{1}. The `deployed_*` columns were added in "
"v1.4.0 for the deployment metadata flowback used by `listPublicBundles()`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:93
msgid "`form_schemas`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:94
msgid ""
"CREATE TABLE form_schemas (\n"
"  id             TEXT        PRIMARY KEY,\n"
"  name           TEXT        NOT NULL,\n"
"  description    TEXT,\n"
"  schema         JSONB       NOT NULL,\n"
"  status         TEXT        DEFAULT 'wip',\n"
"  schema_version INTEGER     NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n"
"  language       VARCHAR(2),                  -- v1.6.0\n"
"  organization   VARCHAR(100),                 -- v1.6.0\n"
"  created_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,\n"
"  updated_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n"
");\n"
"\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_fs_language     ON form_schemas (language)\n"
"  WHERE language IS NOT NULL;\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_fs_organization ON form_schemas (organization)\n"
"  WHERE organization IS NOT NULL;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:114
msgid "`document_templates`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:115
msgid ""
"CREATE TABLE document_templates (\n"
"  id             TEXT        PRIMARY KEY,\n"
"  name           TEXT        NOT NULL,\n"
"  description    TEXT,\n"
"  process_key    TEXT,\n"
"  service_id     TEXT,\n"
"  schema_version INTEGER     NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,\n"
"  zones          JSONB       NOT NULL,\n"
"  bindings       JSONB       NOT NULL DEFAULT '[]',\n"
"  assets         JSONB       NOT NULL DEFAULT '[]',\n"
"  status         TEXT        DEFAULT 'wip',\n"
"  language       VARCHAR(2),                  -- v1.6.0\n"
"  organization   VARCHAR(100),                 -- v1.6.0\n"
"  created_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL,\n"
"  updated_at     TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n"
");\n"
"\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_dt_language     ON document_templates (language)\n"
"  WHERE language IS NOT NULL;\n"
"CREATE INDEX idx_dt_organization ON document_templates (organization)\n"
"  WHERE organization IS NOT NULL;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:141
msgid "Migrations"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:143
msgid ""
"Schema migrations run automatically on backend startup via `migrate()` in "
"`src/db/migrate.ts`, called from `startServer()` in `src/index.ts`. The "
"migration uses inline SQL with `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS` guards, making "
"it idempotent and safe to run on every deploy."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Casset-storage.md:144
msgid ""
"// src/index.ts\n"
"const startServer = async () => {\n"
"  await migrate();  // runs before app.listen()\n"
"  // ...\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

