#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:3
msgid ""
"The backend is a Node.js/Express TypeScript API. It sits between the React "
"frontend and two external services: TriplyDB (SPARQL knowledge graph) and "
"Operaton (DMN execution engine). Its responsibilities are SPARQL querying, "
"DMN chain orchestration, variable mapping between chain steps, and proxying "
"dynamic TriplyDB endpoint calls."
msgstr ""

