#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:9
msgid ""
"All endpoints follow `/v1/*`. Legacy `/api/*` endpoints exist with "
"`Deprecation` response headers for backward compatibility. The version is "
"included in every response via the `API-Version` header, following Dutch "
"Government API Design Rules API-20 and API-57."
msgstr ""

