#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbackend.md:229
msgid ""
"`edocs.service.ts` wraps the OpenText eDOCS REST API. It authenticates once "
"via `POST /connect`, caches the `X-DM-DST` session token, and re-"
