#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:375
msgid ""
"`bpmnService.ts` stores processes as `BpmnProcess` records in PostgreSQL via "
"the backend, using `localStorage` as a synchronous read cache. See [Asset "
"Storage]{1} for the full write-through cache and hydration architecture."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:377
msgid ""
"The `BpmnProcess` type includes three relationship fields added in v1.3.0:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:378
msgid ""
"interface BpmnProcess {\n"
"  // ... existing fields ...\n"
"  bpmnProcessId?: string;                               // <process "
"id=\"...\"> from XML\n"
"  processRole?: 'shell' | 'subprocess' | 'standalone';\n"
"  calledElement?: string;                               // parent shell's "
"bpmnProcessId\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:387
msgid "`bpmnProcessId` is extracted from the XML on save using:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:388
msgid ""
"const extractBpmnProcessId = (xml: string): string => {\n"
"  const match = xml.match(/<(?:bpmn:)?process[^>]+\\bid=\"([^\"]+)\"/);\n"
"  return match?.[1] ?? 'unknown';\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:395
msgid ""
"`ProcessList.tsx` uses `calledElement === shell.bpmnProcessId` to group "
"subprocesses under their parent shell in the hierarchical view."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:397
msgid "Bundle assembly after migration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:399
msgid ""
"`BpmnCanvas.tsx` resolves subprocess XMLs for deployment by matching "
"`calledElement` values from the active BPMN against stored `BpmnProcess` "
"records. After the PostgreSQL migration the lookup continues to work "
"identically — `hydrateFromServer()` ensures the local cache reflects the "
"database state on mount, so the in-memory lookup in `BpmnService.getProcesses"
"()` always has current data."
msgstr ""

