#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:11
msgid "v1.6.0 — Multilingualism & pending-until-Save editing (April 2026)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:13
msgid "**v1.6.0 — New Feature (April 27, 2026)**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:15
msgid "Multilingualism — language and organization metadata"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:17
msgid ""
"BPMN processes, Camunda forms, and document templates now carry an optional "
"ISO 639-1 language code (`en`, `nl`, `de`) and an open-ended organization "
"key. The model is sibling-artefact i18n: each artefact exists once per "
"language, with the LDE deploy modal warning on mixed-language bundles. DMNs "
"stay language-agnostic — variable keys remain stable English so a single DMN "
"serves both English and Dutch sibling BPMNs."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:19
msgid ""
"**Database** — `language VARCHAR(2)` and `organization VARCHAR(100)` columns "
"added to `process_definitions`, `form_schemas`, and `document_templates` "
"with partial indexes; nullable, existing rows coexist as `NULL`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:20
msgid ""
"**BPMN moddle descriptor** — `LanguageMixin` and `OrganizationMixin` "
"extending `bpmn:Process` in `ronlModdleDescriptor.json`; survive `saveXML` "
"round-trip via the existing `ronl` namespace registration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:21
msgid ""
"**List panels** — new `ArtefactListToolbar` (search + language filter + "
"match counter) shared by Process, Form, and Document lists; collapsible "
"organization groups; subprocesses follow their shell's organization "
"regardless of their own tag"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:22
msgid ""
"**Editor footer panel** — uniform pattern across all three editors: "
"`LanguageSelector` and `OrganizationSelector` (with autocomplete from "
"existing organization keys); BPMN footer additionally retains RoPA and DSO "
"selectors"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:23
msgid ""
"**Filename-based language inference on import** — `.bpmn`, `.form`, "
"`.document` files with a `<id>.<lang>.<ext>` suffix are auto-tagged on "
"import; precedence: in-file value → filename → untagged"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:24
msgid ""
"**Form export** — `Export .form` now wraps the form-js schema with top-level "
"`language` and `organization` keys and uses a language-suffixed filename; "
"round-trip integrity for all three artefact types"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:25
msgid ""
"**Deploy-time language consistency check** — amber warning surfaces inline "
"in the deploy modal when a bundle mixes languages, listing the offending "
"codes; mirrors the existing RoPA-missing warning UX"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:27
msgid ""
"**Files:** `packages/backend/src/db/migrate.ts`, `packages/backend/src/db/"
