"DMN files against the RONL DMN+ syntactic layers. It is accessible from the "
"shield icon (🛡) in the sidebar. You can drop any number of .dmn or .xml "
"files onto the validator at once, or add files incrementally — the drop zone "
"remains visible at the top of the panel whenever files are loaded. Files are "
"validated independently and displayed side-by-side for easy comparison."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cchangelog-roadmap.md:443
msgid ""
