#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment-postgresql.md:107
msgid ""
"Warning: SECURITY WARNING: The SSL modes 'prefer', 'require', and 'verify-"
