#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:42
msgid ""
"`useState<DmnEntry[]>([])` holds all loaded files. Each entry is updated "
"immutably by id when its validation completes."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:44
msgid "Key behaviours"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:46
msgid ""
"**Persistence across navigation.** The component is rendered unconditionally "
"in `App.tsx` and hidden with the Tailwind `hidden` class when not active:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:48
msgid ""
"<div className={`flex-1 overflow-hidden flex flex-col ${\n"
"  viewMode === ViewMode.VALIDATE ? '' : 'hidden'\n"
"}`}>\n"
"  <DmnValidator apiBaseUrl={API_BASE_URL} />\n"
"</div>"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:56
msgid ""
"This keeps React from unmounting the component — and therefore from "
"discarding state — when the user switches views."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:58
msgid ""
"**Multi-file drop.** The `addFiles(files)` helper iterates `FileList | "
"File[]`, rejects non-`.dmn`/`.xml` files with a toast, and for each accepted "
"file spawns a `FileReader` that appends a new `DmnEntry` to state on "
"`onload`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:60
msgid ""
"**Concurrent validation.** `validateAll()` calls `validateEntry(id)` for "
"every entry that is not already validating. Each call is an independent "
"`fetch` — they run in parallel."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:62
msgid ""
"**Non-blocking errors.** A fetch or parse failure sets `entry.error` and "
"clears `entry.isValidating`. It never throws or blocks other entries."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:64
msgid "Component tree"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdmn-validator-implementation.md:66
msgid ""
"DmnValidator\n"
"├── Header (title, \"Validate all\", \"Clear all\")\n"
"├── Drop zone (always mounted, compact when entries exist)\n"
"├── Drop error toast (auto-dismisses after 4 s)\n"
"└── Entry cards (horizontal scrollable row)\n"
"    └── EntryCard (one per DmnEntry)\n"
"        ├── Card header (filename, size, Validate, ×)\n"
"        └── Card body\n"
"            ├── \"Press Validate to run checks\" placeholder\n"
"            ├── Validation spinner\n"
"            ├── Error message\n"
"            └── Result\n"
"                ├── Summary badge (valid/invalid + E/W/I counts)\n"
"                └── LayerSection × 5\n"
"                    └── IssueRow × n"
msgstr ""

