#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdocument-composer.md:130
msgid ""
"useEffect(() => {\n"
"  editor?.setEditable(!readonly);\n"
