msgid "BPMN Modeler integration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:96
msgid ""
"`DmnTemplateSelector.tsx` loads DRD templates alongside regular DMNs when a "
"`BusinessRuleTask` is selected:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:98
msgid ""
"const loadOptions = async () => {\n"
"  // Fetch regular DMNs from API\n"
"  const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE_URL}/v1/dmns?endpoint=${endpoint}"
"`);\n"
"  const dmnArray = data.data.dmns;\n"
"\n"
"  // Load local DRD templates\n"
"  const userTemplates = getUserTemplates(endpoint);\n"
"  const drdOptions = userTemplates\n"
"    .filter(t => t.isDrd && t.drdEntryPointId)\n"
"    .map(t => ({\n"
"      identifier: t.drdEntryPointId,\n"
"      title: `${t.name} (DRD)`,\n"
"      isDrd: true,\n"
"      originalChain: t.drdOriginalChain,\n"
"    }));\n"
"\n"
"  setOptions({ drds: drdOptions, dmns: dmnArray });\n"
"};"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cdrd-generation.md:119
msgid ""
"Selecting a DRD option sets `camunda:decisionRef` to the `drdEntryPointId`. "
"Operaton uses this to look up and evaluate the deployed DRD."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:1
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\developer\\edocs-integration.md:1"
msgid "eDOCS Integration"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:3
msgid ""
"The LDE backend integrates with **OpenText eDOCS** — the document management "
"system used by Province of Flevoland — to automatically file process "
"documents into project workspaces as part of the RIP Phase 1 workflow."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:5
msgid ""
"The integration uses the **external task pattern**: Operaton polls the LDE "
"backend worker via `fetchAndLock` rather than the backend calling Operaton. "
"This keeps the coupling loose and makes the integration resilient to "
"temporary eDOCS unavailability."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:9
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\developer\\edocs-integration.md:9"
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:11
msgid ""
"sequenceDiagram\n"
"    participant O as Operaton\n"
"    participant W as ExternalTaskWorker\n"
"    participant E as EdocsService\n"
"    participant D as eDOCS REST API\n"
"\n"
"    O->>W: fetchAndLock (topic: rip-edocs-workspace)\n"
"    W->>E: ensureWorkspace(projectNumber, projectName)\n"
"    E->>D: POST /connect → X-DM-DST token\n"
"    E->>D: GET /workspaces?filter=projectNumber\n"
"    D-->>E: workspace found / not found\n"
"    alt workspace not found\n"
"        E->>D: POST /workspaces\n"
"        D-->>E: { id: 2993897 }\n"
"    end\n"
"    E-->>W: { workspaceId, workspaceName, created }\n"
"    W->>O: complete task (sets edocsWorkspaceId)\n"
"\n"
"    O->>W: fetchAndLock (topic: rip-edocs-document)\n"
"    W->>E: uploadDocument(workspaceId, filename, content, metadata)\n"
"    E->>D: POST /documents (with _restapi.ref.id: workspaceId)\n"
"    D-->>E: { DOCNUMBER: \"2993898\" }\n"
"    E-->>W: { documentId, documentNumber }\n"
"    W->>O: complete task (sets edocsIntakeReportId)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:40
