msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:44
msgid ""
"Wraps the eDOCS REST API with session token caching and automatic re-"
"authentication."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:46
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:48
msgid ""
"The service authenticates once via `POST /connect`, which returns an `X-DM-"
"DST` session token. The token is cached in memory and attached to every "
"subsequent request via an Axios request interceptor. On a `401` or `403` "
"response the service re-authenticates once and retries the original request "
"automatically."
msgstr ""

