msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:106
msgid ""
"The Chain Composer uses `@dnd-kit/core` for drag detection and `@dnd-kit/"
"sortable` for reordering within the composer. DMN cards in the Available "
"DMNs list are `Draggable`; the Chain Composer area is a `Droppable`. Cards "
