#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cfrontend.md:112
msgid ""
"`sparqlService.ts` handles query execution via the backend proxy endpoint (`/"
"v1/triplydb/query`). For direct SPARQL endpoints in development, it includes "
"a CORS fallback. Result parsing handles both standard `application/sparql-"
"results+json` and variations in binding formats."
