msgid ""
"`templateService.ts` provides the localStorage interface for both chain "
"templates and BPMN processes. All storage keys are prefixed with `linkeddata-"
"explorer-`. Templates are namespaced by endpoint URL so switching endpoints "
"does not surface templates from another dataset."
