#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:129
msgid ""
"bpmn_process_id          | process_level | status\n"
"----------------------------------+---------------+--------\n"
" AwbShellProcess                  | shell         | active\n"
" AwbZorgtoeslagProcess            | shell         | active\n"
" TreeFellingPermitSubProcess      | subprocess    | active\n"
" ZorgtoeslagProvisionalSubProcess | subprocess    | active\n"
"(4 rows)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:139
msgid "Verify the public endpoint"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:140
msgid ""
"curl \"http://localhost:3001/v1/ropa/public?organisation=flevoland\" | jq "
"'.data | length'"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:144
msgid ""
"Should return `4`. If you get `0`, the `controller_name` values in the "
"seeded records do not contain \"flevoland\" — re-run the seed after "
"verifying the controller names in `src/db/seed-ropa.ts`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:146
msgid "Test the public site locally"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:148
msgid ""
"`packages/ropa-site/index.html` has the API URL hardcoded. For local "
"development change it to the local backend:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:149
msgid ""
"const API_URL =\n"
"  'http://localhost:3001/v1/ropa/public?organisation=flevoland';"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:154
msgid "Open the file directly in a browser (`file://`) or serve it:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:155
msgid ""
"cd packages/ropa-site\n"
"npx serve ."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:160
msgid ""
"!!! warning \"CORS when opening as file://\" When `index.html` is opened "
"directly from disk, the browser sends `Origin: null`. The global CORS "
"middleware rejects `null` origins. The path-aware CORS fix in `index.ts` "
"that serves `/v1/ropa/public` with `origin: '*'` bypasses this — but only if "
"that fix is in place. If you see a CORS error when opening from `file://`, "
"confirm `index.ts` has the path-aware cors middleware, not just the route-"
"level cors in `ropa.public.routes.ts`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Clocal-development.md:163
msgid ""
"!!! note \"Revert before committing\" Remember to revert `const API_URL` to "
"the ACC or production URL before committing `packages/ropa-site/index.html`."
msgstr ""

