#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cropa-records.md:147
msgid ""
"The public route applies `cors({ origin: '*', methods: ['GET', 'OPTIONS'] })"
"` at the route level. However, the global CORS middleware in `index.ts` "
"evaluates origins before route handlers are reached. The solution is a path-"
"aware middleware in `index.ts` that bypasses the origin whitelist for `/v1/"
"ropa/public`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cropa-records.md:148
msgid ""
"app.use((req, res, next) => {\n"
"  if (req.path.startsWith('/v1/ropa/public')) {\n"
"    cors({ origin: '*', methods: ['GET', 'OPTIONS'] })(req, res, next);\n"
"  } else {\n"
"    cors(corsOptions)(req, res, next);\n"
"  }\n"
"});"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cropa-records.md:158
msgid ""
"The same pattern applies to the preflight `app.options('*', ...)` handler."
msgstr ""

