#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:30
msgid ""
"Shell processes are top-level entries. Their subprocesses are indented "
"beneath them with a tree connector. Standalone processes — those with no "
"parent-child relationship — appear as top-level entries without indentation."
msgstr ""

