msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:19
msgid "A **Validate** button to trigger validation for that file individually"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:20
msgid ""
"A **Validate all** button in the header to validate all loaded files at once"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:21
msgid ""
"The validation result with a summary badge and collapsible layer sections"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:22
msgid "A remove (×) button to dismiss the file"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdmn-validator.md:24
msgid ""
"Navigation state is preserved: switching to another view (SPARQL editor, "
"chain builder, etc.) and returning does not clear the loaded files or their "
