"and Chain Builder."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:16
msgid ""
"**Left panel** — Document list. Shows all documents stored in `localStorage` "
"with create, rename, delete, and **Save as…** actions. An **EXAMPLE** badge "
"marks the read-only seed document; user-created documents carry a **WIP** "
"badge."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cdocument-composer.md:17
msgid ""
"**Centre panel** — Zone canvas. Renders the document zones in A4-style "
"layout. Blocks are dragged onto zones from the left panel's Content library, "
"and can be reordered or moved between zones by dragging."
