#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cform-editor.md:102
msgid ""
"A file named `<form-id>.<lang>.form` (e.g. `capacity-claim-intake.nl.form`) "
