msgid ""
"`libxmljs2.parseXml()` throws a `SyntaxError` — the file is not well-formed "
"XML"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:29
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:29"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:29
msgid ""
"DMN files are XML documents. A parser error means the file cannot be read at "
"all — not by the validator, not by Operaton, not by any other DMN tooling. "
"This is the most fundamental failure mode."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:29
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:29"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:29
msgid ""
"Open the file in a text editor or XML validator. Common causes: unclosed "
"tags, illegal characters in attribute values, missing XML declaration "
"encoding, byte-order mark (BOM) at the start of the file. The `line` and "
"`column` fields on the issue pinpoint the exact location."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:38
