#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:40
msgid "The root element is not named `definitions`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:40
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:40"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:40
msgid ""
"The DMN 1.x specification mandates `<definitions>` as the document root. A "
"different root element means the file is either not a DMN file, is a "
"fragment, or has been corrupted."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:40
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:40"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:40
msgid ""
"Ensure the file starts with `<definitions xmlns=\"https://www.omg.org/spec/"
"DMN/20191111/MODEL/\" ...>`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:49
