#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:62
msgid ""
"The DMN specification requires a `name` on `<definitions>`. Operaton uses "
"this name in its deployment UI. A missing name makes it harder to identify a "
"model in the engine and in TriplyDB metadata."
