msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:84
msgid ""
"A DMN file with no decisions contains no executable logic. This typically "
"indicates an empty template, a partially authored file, or a file that only "
"contains `<inputData>` definitions without the associated decisions."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:84
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:84"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:84
msgid ""
"Add at least one `<decision>` element, or verify that the correct file was "
"uploaded."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:93
msgid "Layer 2 — Business Rules (BIZ-*)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:95
msgid ""
"Layer 2 checks the structural correctness of decision table definitions: "
"that enumerations are valid, that type declarations are present, that rule "
"rows are internally consistent, and that hit-policy constraints are not "
"violated by the static structure of the table."
msgstr ""

