#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:371
msgid ""
"An `<inputData>` element exists in the document but is not referenced by any "
"`<informationRequirement>`. Only fires in DRDs — models with more than one "
"`<decision>` element or at least one `<informationRequirement>`. In "
"standalone single-decision DMNs, `<inputData>` elements serve as input "
"contract declarations for CPSV/publishing purposes and do not require wiring."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:371
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:371"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:371
msgid ""
"An orphaned `<inputData>` element in a DRD declares an input that no "
"decision uses. It adds clutter to the DRD, makes the model harder to "
"understand, and causes the CPSV Editor to generate `cpsv:Input` metadata for "
"an input that has no effect on any decision outcome."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:371
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:371"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:371
msgid ""
"Connect the `<inputData>` element to a decision via `<informationRequirement>"
"`, or remove it from the model."
msgstr ""

