#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:382
msgid ""
"An `<inputData>` element has a `name` attribute that does not match the "
"`name` of its child `<variable>` element"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:382
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:382"
msgid "**Rationale**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:382
msgid ""
"Operaton resolves inputs by variable name at runtime. A mismatch between the "
"`<inputData name=\"...\">` and its `<variable name=\"...\">` is a common "
"source of \"my rule never fires\" bugs where the input evaluates to null."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:382
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\reference\\dmn-validation-reference.md:382"
msgid "**Fix**"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Creference%5Cdmn-validation-reference.md:382
msgid ""
"Align the `<variable name=\"...\">` with the `<inputData name=\"...\">`."
msgstr ""

