"The `typeRef` on a `<variable>` declares the FEEL type of the value it "
"represents. Without it, consuming decisions in a DRD cannot perform type-"
"safe input binding, and the chain builder in the Linked Data Explorer cannot "
"verify type compatibility between linked DMNs."
msgstr ""

