msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:115
msgid ""
"**Fit to viewport** button — centres and scales the diagram to fill the "
