msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\user-guide\\bpmn-modeler.md:120"
msgid "Storage"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:122
msgid ""
"Processes are stored in PostgreSQL via the LDE backend and cached in browser "
"`localStorage` for instant access. On editor load, the service fetches the "
"authoritative list from the server and replaces the local cache. If the "
"backend is unreachable, the local cache is used as a fallback without any "
"error surfaced to the user."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:124
msgid ""
"Example processes (`readonly: true`) are seeded from `public/examples/` on "
"the frontend and are never written to the database."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:126
msgctxt "C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer\\user-guide\\bpmn-modeler.md:126"
msgid "See [Asset Storage]{1} for the full architecture."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:128
msgid ""
"Click **Export** to download a `.bpmn` file for deployment to Operaton. You "
"can also deploy directly from the Modeler using the **Deploy** button. See "
"[Deploying to Operaton]{1} above."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:132
