#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:136
msgid "`UserTask` for application submission"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:137
msgid ""
"`BusinessRuleTask` (Assess Felling Permit) linked to `TreeFellingDecision`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:138
msgid "`ExclusiveGateway` routing on the decision outcome"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cbpmn-modeler.md:139
